c; Hồng Phong,&nbsp; Quận 10, TP. HCM</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Giờ mở cửa:</strong>&nbsp;09:00 &ndash; 22:00</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn3.ivivu.com/2019/06/Top-15-quan-chay-Sai-Gon-ngon-quen-loi-ve-ivivu-3.jpg\" target=\"_blank\"><img alt=\"Ảnh: lanwiththi\" height=\"1080\" src=\"https://cdn3.ivivu.com/2019/06/Top-15-quan-chay-Sai-Gon-ngon-quen-loi-ve-ivivu-3.jpg\" title=\"Ảnh: lanwiththi\" width=\"1080\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ảnh: lanwiththi</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>4. Qu&aacute;n chay chị Cũ</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Địa chỉ:</strong>&nbsp;4/7 Trần Đ&igrave;nh Xu (Số 18 Cũ Dời Qua Đối Diện) P. C&ocirc; Giang,&nbsp; Quận 1, TP. HCM</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Giờ mở cửa:</strong>&nbsp;24/7</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn3.ivivu.com/2019/06/43690818_1806578299455102_2658078701702348800_n.jpg\" target=\"_blank\"><img alt=\"Ảnh: thon.foodie\" height=\"1080\" src=\"https://cdn3.ivivu.com/2019/06/43690818_1806578299455102_2658078701702348800_n.jpg\" title=\"Ảnh: thon.foodie\" width=\"1080\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ảnh: thon.foodie</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>5. Việt Chay</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Địa chỉ:</strong>&nbsp;290/21A Nam Kỳ Khởi Nghĩa,&nbsp; Quận 3, TP. HCM</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Giờ mở cửa:</strong>&nbsp;10:00 &ndash; 22:00</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn3.ivivu.com/2019/06/46305329_509322909555550_1205824055605723136_n.jpg\" target=\"_blank\"><img alt=\"Ảnh: thon.foodie\" height=\"1080\" src=\"https://cdn3.ivivu.com/2019/06/46305329_509322909555550_1205824055605723136_n.jpg\" title=\"Ảnh: thon.foodie\" width=\"1080\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ảnh: thon.foodie</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>6. Qu&aacute;n chay Định &Yacute;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><iframe height=\"311\" scrolling=\"no\" src=\"https://www.ivivu.com/hothotel/?placeslug=an-choi-am-thuc&amp;number=1&amp;width=481\" width=\"100%\"></iframe></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Địa chỉ:</strong>&nbsp;171B Cống Quỳnh,&nbsp; Quận 1, TP. HCM</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Giờ mở cửa:</strong>&nbsp;08:00 &ndash; 22:00</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a hr